"Change Set:		9329Compiler-ar.118Compiler-ar.118:Provide a defaultResumeValue for UndeclaredVariableWarning.Compiler-ar.117:Better progress in Compiler>>recompileAll."!!Compiler class methodsFor: 'utilities' stamp: 'ar 2/12/2010 00:54'!recompileAll	"Compiler recompileAll"	"Recompile all classes and traits in the system"	Smalltalk forgetDoIts.	Smalltalk allClassesAndTraits 		do: [:classOrTrait | classOrTrait compileAll] 		displayingProgress:[:classOrTrait| 'Recompiling ', classOrTrait]! !!UndeclaredVariableWarning methodsFor: 'initialize-release' stamp: 'ar 2/13/2010 15:21'!defaultResumeValue	"Answer the value that by default should be returned if the exception is resumed"	^true! !